To make it look better, you can create a styles.css file for the basic styling:

body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background-color: #f4f4f9;
}

.container {
    width: 80%;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

header {
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    color: white;
    padding: 20px 0;
    text-align: center;
}

